					Full Description



		Tatt Giap Group Berhad is an investment holding company. The Company is engaged in manufacturing and trading of various steel products, which include stainless steel pipes, tubes and bars, electro-galvanized steel, perforated metal products and other ferrous and non-ferrous metal products. Its geographical segments include Malaysia, Asia (excluding Malaysia), the United States of America and Europe. It supplies its products to various industrial and building sectors in Malaysia and exports to Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN) countries, India, Australia, the United States and the Middle East. Its subsidiaries include Tatt Giap Hardware Sdn. Bhd., which is an importer, wholesaler and retailer of stainless steel products; Superinox Pipe Industry Sdn. Bhd., which manufactures and distributes Superinox stainless steel pipes and tubes; Superinox Max Fittings Industry Sdn. Bhd., which is engaged in manufacturing and distribution of Superinox stainless steel fittings and pipes
» Full Overview of TATG.KL







