Group
Overview

Tatt Giap Group
Berhad was incorporated in Malaysia in June 1978 as an
importer and stockist of stainless steel materials. It has since then
enlarged its product range through active sourcing and building up of
strong relationships with stainless steel producers worldwide.
 
  
 


 



    

 















 

  

 
 
 

 
 














 
 








