Company Description                    




                        Tatt Giap Group Berhad engages in the steel and stainless steel processing business. The products include stainless steel pipes and tubes, cold drawn and polished carbon steel/stainless steel bars, and electro galvanising steel coils. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Perai.                    


